def RFR_model(df_train, df_val, df_test,model_features):
    regr = RandomForestRegressor(random_state =      42,
                                 n_jobs =            -1,
                                 criterion  =       'squared_error',
                                 n_estimators =      500, 
                                 max_depth =         30, 
                                 min_samples_split=  27,
                                 bootstrap =         'True', 
                                 warm_start =        'False',
                                 oob_score =         'False',
                                 max_features =      'auto', 
                                 min_samples_leaf =   1, 
                                 max_samples =        268032, # :) 
                                 max_leaf_nodes =     None,
                                 verbose =            1)
    regr.fit(X_train, y_train)
    y_pred_train =  regr.predict(X_train)
    y_pred_test  =  regr.predict(X_test)
    y_pred_val   =  regr.predict(X_val)
    y_pred_test_combined = regr.predict(X_test_combined)   
    print('\n--- Test Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_test, y_pred_test))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred_test))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred_test)))   
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_test, y_pred_test))  
    print('\n--- Val Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_val, y_pred_val))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_val, y_pred_val))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_val, y_pred_val)))   
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_val, y_pred_val))
    print('\n--- Train Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_train, y_pred_train))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_train, y_pred_train))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_train, y_pred_train)))
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_train, y_pred_train)) 
    print('\n--- Combined Test Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined)))
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined))   
    pprint(regr.get_params(deep=True))

WHICH MEANS: - We should use the location features in our next analysis !




All of the Code is shown below...¶

Approach:

  • use: RandomForestRegressor regression model

  • start tuning with: Random Search with Cross Validation

  • refine your search with: GridSearchCV. multiple layers of GridSearch...

  • sanity check

  • compare to default random forest regressor parameters output

  • tune tune tune

  • If you have the horsepower, use the horsepower - 64GB, above-average GPU, AMD hard core CPU

def RFR_model_base(X_train,y_train,X_val,y_val,X_test,y_test,X_test_combined, y_test_combined): 
    start_time = time.time()
    
    regr = RandomForestRegressor(random_state=42, 
                                 n_jobs=-1)
    
    regr.fit(X_train, y_train)
    y_pred_train =  regr.predict(X_train)
    y_pred_test  =  regr.predict(X_test)
    y_pred_val   =  regr.predict(X_val)
    y_pred_test_combined = regr.predict(X_test_combined)
    print('\n--- Test Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_test, y_pred_test))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred_test))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred_test)))   
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_test, y_pred_test))  
    print('\n--- Val Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_val, y_pred_val))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_val, y_pred_val))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_val, y_pred_val)))   
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_val, y_pred_val))
    print('\n--- Train Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_train, y_pred_train))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_train, y_pred_train))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_train, y_pred_train)))
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_train, y_pred_train)) 
    
    print('\n--- Combined Test Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined)))
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined))   
    print('\nModel Hyperparameters Definitions:')
    # pprint(regr.get_params(deep=True))
    for k,v in regr.get_params(deep=True).items():
        print(k, "->", v)
    print("\n--- %s seconds ---" % round((time.time() - start_time)))

def grid_search_1(X_train,y_train,X_val,y_val,X_test,y_test,X_test_combined, y_test_combined): 

    start_time = time.time()
    rf = RandomForestRegressor(random_state=42, n_jobs=-1)
    
    param_grid = [{'n_estimators': [5,50], 
                   'criterion': ['squared_error'], 
                   # 'max_features': [5,10,20, 25],
                   # 'max_depth': [3, 4, 5, 10, 15, 20], 
                   # 'min_samples_leaf': [1,2,5,10], 
                   'bootstrap': [True]}]
    
    grid_search_rf = GridSearchCV(estimator = rf, 
                                  param_grid = param_grid, 
                                  cv=3, 
                                  n_jobs = -1,
                                  verbose=1,
                                  return_train_score=True,
                                  scoring='r2')
                                  # neg_mean_squared_error') # 
    grid_search_rf.fit(X_train, y_train)
    print("\nBest parameters set found on Cross Validation: ***")
    print(grid_search_rf.best_params_)
    print('\nBest Estimator:\n', grid_search_rf.best_estimator_)
    print("\nCross Validation R\u00b2 score ..... ", grid_search_rf.best_score_.round(3))
    print("\n--- %s seconds ---" % round((time.time() - start_time)))

def RFR_model(X_train,y_train,X_val,y_val,X_test,y_test,X_test_combined, y_test_combined): 
    start_time = time.time()
    
    regr = RandomForestRegressor(random_state=42,
                                 n_jobs=22,
                                 n_estimators=300, 
                                 max_depth=30,
                                 max_features=30,
                                 min_samples_leaf=2)
    
    regr.fit(X_train, y_train)
    y_pred_train =  regr.predict(X_train)
    y_pred_test  =  regr.predict(X_test)
    y_pred_val   =  regr.predict(X_val)
    y_pred_test_combined = regr.predict(X_test_combined)
    print('\n--- Test Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_test, y_pred_test))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred_test))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred_test)))   
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_test, y_pred_test))  
    print('\n--- Val Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_val, y_pred_val))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_val, y_pred_val))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_val, y_pred_val)))   
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_val, y_pred_val))
    print('\n--- Train Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_train, y_pred_train))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_train, y_pred_train))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_train, y_pred_train)))
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_train, y_pred_train)) 
    
    print('\n--- Combined Test Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined)))
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined))   
    print('\nModel Hyperparameters Definitions:')
    # pprint(regr.get_params(deep=True))
    for k,v in regr.get_params(deep=True).items():
        print(k, "->", v)
    print("\n--- %s seconds ---" % round((time.time() - start_time)))

#  RandomForestRegressor(max_depth=40, max_features='sqrt', min_samples_split=22,
#                       n_estimators=500, n_jobs=22, random_state=42)
    
def RFR_model(X_train,y_train,X_val,y_val,X_test,y_test,X_test_combined, y_test_combined): 
    start_time = time.time()
    
    
    #   n_estimators = number of trees in the foreset
    #   max_features = max number of features considered for splitting a node
    #   max_depth = max number of levels in each decision tree
    #   min_samples_split = min number of data points placed in a node before the node is split
    #   min_samples_leaf = min number of data points allowed in a leaf node
    #   bootstrap = method for sampling data points (with or without replacement)



    regr = RandomForestRegressor(random_state=42,
                                 n_jobs=-1,
                                 n_estimators=1000, 
                                 max_depth=40,
                                 min_samples_split=22,
                                 max_features='sqrt',
                                 min_samples_leaf=2, 
                                 bootstrap = True)
    
    regr.fit(X_train, y_train)
    y_pred_train =  regr.predict(X_train)
    y_pred_test  =  regr.predict(X_test)
    y_pred_val   =  regr.predict(X_val)
    y_pred_test_combined = regr.predict(X_test_combined)
    print('\n--- Test Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_test, y_pred_test))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred_test))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred_test)))   
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_test, y_pred_test))  
    print('\n--- Val Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_val, y_pred_val))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_val, y_pred_val))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_val, y_pred_val)))   
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_val, y_pred_val))
    print('\n--- Train Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_train, y_pred_train))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_train, y_pred_train))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_train, y_pred_train)))
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_train, y_pred_train)) 
    
    print('\n--- Combined Test Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined)))
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined))   
    print('\nModel Hyperparameters Definitions:')
    # pprint(regr.get_params(deep=True))
    for k,v in regr.get_params(deep=True).items():
        print(k, "->", v)
    print("\n--- %s seconds ---" % round((time.time() - start_time)))

def RFR_model(X_train,y_train,X_val,y_val,X_test,y_test,X_test_combined, y_test_combined): 
    start_time = time.time()
    
    
    #   n_estimators = number of trees in the foreset
    #   max_features = max number of features considered for splitting a node
    #   max_depth = max number of levels in each decision tree
    #   min_samples_split = min number of data points placed in a node before the node is split
    #   min_samples_leaf = min number of data points allowed in a leaf node
    #   bootstrap = method for sampling data points (with or without replacement)



    regr = RandomForestRegressor(random_state=42,
                                 n_jobs=-1,
                                 n_estimators=700, 
                                 max_depth=40,
                                 min_samples_split=22,
                                 max_features='auto',
                                 min_samples_leaf=2, 
                                 bootstrap = False)   # bootstrap is true 
    
    regr.fit(X_train, y_train)
    y_pred_train =  regr.predict(X_train)
    y_pred_test  =  regr.predict(X_test)
    y_pred_val   =  regr.predict(X_val)
    y_pred_test_combined = regr.predict(X_test_combined)
    print('\n--- Test Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_test, y_pred_test))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred_test))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred_test)))   
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_test, y_pred_test))  
    print('\n--- Val Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_val, y_pred_val))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_val, y_pred_val))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_val, y_pred_val)))   
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_val, y_pred_val))
    print('\n--- Train Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_train, y_pred_train))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_train, y_pred_train))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_train, y_pred_train)))
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_train, y_pred_train)) 
    
    print('\n--- Combined Test Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined)))
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined))   
    # print('\nModel Hyperparameters Definitions:')
    #     # pprint(regr.get_params(deep=True))
    #     for k,v in regr.get_params(deep=True).items():
    #         print(k, "->", v)
    print("\n--- %s seconds ---" % round((time.time() - start_time)))

def RFR_model(X_train,y_train,X_val,y_val,X_test,y_test,X_test_combined, y_test_combined, incr): 
    
    regr = RandomForestRegressor(random_state=42,
                                 n_jobs=-1,
                                 n_estimators=500, 
                                 max_depth=30, 
                                 min_samples_split=27,
                                 bootstrap='True', 
                                 warm_start = 'False', 
                                 verbose=1, 
                                 min_samples_leaf=incr)
    
                                 # max_features='sqrt',
                                 # min_samples_leaf=2
              
    print('\n\nmin_samples_leaf:', incr)
    
    #  'ccp_alpha': 0.0,
    #  'criterion': 'squared_error',
    #  'max_features': 'auto',
    #  'max_leaf_nodes': None,
    #  'max_samples': None,
    #  'min_samples_leaf': 1,
    #  'min_weight_fraction_leaf': 0.0,

    print('\n\nmin_samples_split: ', incr)
    regr.fit(X_train, y_train)
    y_pred_train =  regr.predict(X_train)
    y_pred_test  =  regr.predict(X_test)
    y_pred_val   =  regr.predict(X_val)
    y_pred_test_combined = regr.predict(X_test_combined)
    print('\n--- Test Set ---')
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_test, y_pred_test))  
    print('\n--- Val Set ---')
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_val, y_pred_val))
    print('\n--- Train Set ---')
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_train, y_pred_train)) 
    print('\n--- Combined Test Set ---')
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined)) 
    
    pprint(regr.get_params(deep=True))

for i in [1,2,3,4,5]:
    RFR_model(X_train,y_train,X_val,y_val,X_test,y_test,X_test_combined, y_test_combined, i)

def RFR_model(df_train, df_val, df_test,model_features):
    regr = RandomForestRegressor(random_state =      42,
                                 n_jobs =            -1,
                                 criterion  =       'squared_error',
                                 n_estimators =      500, 
                                 max_depth =         30, 
                                 min_samples_split=  27,
                                 bootstrap =         'True', 
                                 warm_start =        'False',
                                 oob_score =         'False',
                                 max_features =      'auto', 
                                 min_samples_leaf =   1, 
                                 max_samples =        268032, # :) 
                                 max_leaf_nodes =     None,
                                 verbose =            1)
    regr.fit(X_train, y_train)
    y_pred_train =  regr.predict(X_train)
    y_pred_test  =  regr.predict(X_test)
    y_pred_val   =  regr.predict(X_val)
    y_pred_test_combined = regr.predict(X_test_combined)   
    print('\n--- Test Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_test, y_pred_test))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred_test))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred_test)))   
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_test, y_pred_test))  
    print('\n--- Val Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_val, y_pred_val))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_val, y_pred_val))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_val, y_pred_val)))   
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_val, y_pred_val))
    print('\n--- Train Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_train, y_pred_train))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_train, y_pred_train))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_train, y_pred_train)))
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_train, y_pred_train)) 
    print('\n--- Combined Test Set ---')
    print('Mean Absolute Error: ... %.5f' % mean_absolute_error(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined))
    print("Mean Squared Error:..... %.5f" % mean_squared_error(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined))
    print('RMSE: .................. %.5f' % np.sqrt(mean_squared_error(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined)))
    print("Coeff of det (R^2):..... %.5f" % r2_score(y_test_combined, y_pred_test_combined))   
    pprint(regr.get_params(deep=True))
